column2: The coronation sword of the Holy Roman Emperors.
This sword became the original sword of what became the Greenswords. Prince Paul Angelo de los Reyes had forged this sword and even plated it in copper. As time went on, the copper had turned green.
This character descends from Paul Angelo de los Reyes, the first Baron of Caloocan.
